#
# V2ME Cleanup 1.0.3b by Bob Bobington and Dr, configured for GFM
#
# Features:
#
#	-Nearly invisible cleanup tag
#	-Zero performance degradation
#	-Immersion will not be ruined, player interaction with cleanup is kept to an absolute minimum
#	-Multiple stability improvements and bug fixes
#	-Easy to customize for new content
#	-Handles backend tasks (i.e. setting govflags, invention flags, etc) on a daily, monthly, or yearly tick, as needed
#	-Handles vassal interactions with one decision instead of hundreds
#
# Notable bugs addressed:
#
#	-Ghost units and ships of non-existing nations cleaned monthly
#	-Prevent uncivs from gaining colonial states/capitals incorrectly
#	-Prevent countries with slavery outlawed from having bugged slave states
#	-Prevents existing countries from having non-existing overlords
#	-Prevents existing countries from having non-existing vassals (disabled by default, this is intended in some mods)
#
# Upcoming features (TBA):
#	-Permanent fix to craftsmen exploit/bug, without player interaction
#	-Dynamically adressing the liquidity crisis, effectively
#
# Most Recent Version Change:
#	-1.0.3b: GFM Version Only, Added Indochina Organization
#


country_event = {
	id = 477877787
	title = "AI: Daily Cleanup Check"
	desc = "AI: Daily Cleanup Check"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Checking..."
		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					exists = BOR
					NOT = { BOR = { government = absolute_monarchy } }
					NOT = { BOR = { government = prussian_constitutionalism } }
					NOT = { BOR = { government = hms_government } }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				BOR = { all_core = { add_core = FRA remove_core = BOR } change_tag = FRA }
			}
		}
		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					exists = SPC
					NOT = { SPC = { government = absolute_monarchy } }
					NOT = { SPC = { government = prussian_constitutionalism } }
					NOT = { SPC = { government = hms_government } }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				SPC = {
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_1
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_2
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_3
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_4
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_5
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_6
					remove_country_modifier = fueros_unresolved_7
					remove_country_modifier = carlist_distributism
					remove_country_modifier = marotist_reforms
					any_owned = {
						remove_province_modifier = fueros_autonomy
						remove_province_modifier = fueros_autonomy_2
						remove_province_modifier = fueros_autonomy_3
						remove_province_modifier = fueros_autonomy_4
					}
					all_core = {
						add_core = SPA
						remove_core = SPC
					}
					change_tag = SPA
				}
			}
		}
		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					SOV = {
						exists = yes
						NOT = {
							government = proletarian_dictatorship
							exists = RUS
						}
					}
				}
			}
			owner = {
				SOV = { change_tag = RUS }
			}
		}
		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					SWI = {
						ai = no
						has_country_modifier = neutrality_modifier
						OR = {
							any_greater_power = { military_access = SWI }
							any_neighbor_country = { NOT = { vassal_of = SWI } military_access = SWI }
							sphere_owner = { military_access = SWI }
							AND = {
								num_of_allies = 1
								NOT = { NCT = { alliance_with = SWI } }
							}
							AND = {
								num_of_allies = 2
								NCT = { exists = yes alliance_with = SWI }
							}
							war = yes
						}
					}
				}
			}
			owner = {
				any_country = {
					limit = {
						exists = yes
						NOT = { vassal_of = SWI }
						OR = {
							military_access = SWI
							alliance_with = SWI
						}
					}
					relation = { who = SWI value = -125 }
				}
				any_country = {
					limit = {
						exists = yes
						alliance_with = SWI
						NOT = { vassal_of = SWI }
					}
					leave_alliance = SWI
				}
				any_country = {
					limit = {
						exists = yes
						war_with = SWI
					}
					end_war = SWI
				}
				any_country = {
					limit = {
						exists = yes
						military_access = SWI
						NOT = { vassal_of = SWI }
					}
					end_military_access = SWI
				}
			}
		}

		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					OR = {
						FRA = { truce_with = PRU has_country_modifier = rhine_crisis }
						BOR = { truce_with = PRU has_country_modifier = rhine_crisis }
					}
					575 = { OR = { owned_by = PRU owned_by = NGF owned_by = GER owned_by = GCF owned_by = AUS owned_by = SGF } }
					PRU = { is_disarmed = no }
					NOT = { has_global_flag = clean_up_france_lost_rhine_crisis }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				set_global_flag = clean_up_france_lost_rhine_crisis
				any_country = {
					limit = {
						primary_culture = french
						is_greater_power = yes
						exists = yes
					}
					country_event = 99993
				}
			}
		}
        random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					OR = {
						FRA = { any_owned_province = { is_core = BOR } }
						any_owned_province = { is_core = BOR }
					}
					FRA = { exists = yes }
					BOR = { exists = no }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				BOR = {
					all_core = { remove_core = BOR add_core = FRA }
				}
			}
		}
        random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					OR = {
						BOR = { any_owned_province = { is_core = FRA } }
						any_owned_province = { is_core = FRA }
					}
					BOR = { exists = yes }
					FRA = { exists = no }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				FRA = {
					all_core = { remove_core = FRA add_core = BOR }
				}
			}
        }
        random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					QNG = {
						has_global_flag = taiping_has_happened
						NOT = { has_global_flag = tpg_war_started }
						NOT = { has_country_modifier = no_more_war }
					}
					NOT = { has_global_flag = tpg_war_started }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				QNG = {
					set_global_flag = tpg_war_started
					country_event = 99931
				}
			}
		}
		#updating missing flags
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				exists = yes
				NOT = {
					has_country_flag = existing_country
				}
			}
			set_country_flag = existing_country
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				has_country_flag = existing_country
				exists = no
			}
			clr_country_flag = existing_country
		}

		#native assimilation cleanup
		any_country = {
            limit = {
                has_country_flag = native_assimilation_enacted
				exists = yes
                NOT = { has_country_modifier = native_assimilation_act_policy }
            }
            clr_country_flag = native_assimilation_enacted
        }

		#pay owed steamers
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				check_variable = { which = owed_ammunition value = 5 }
				ammunition = 5
				exists = yes
			}
			ammunition = -5
			change_variable = { which = owed_ammunition value = -5 }
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				check_variable = { which = owed_small_arms value = 5 }
				small_arms = 5
				exists = yes
			}
			small_arms = -5
			change_variable = { which = owed_small_arms value = -5 }
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				check_variable = { which = owed_steamers value = 5 }
				steamer_convoy = 5
				exists = yes
			}
			steamer_convoy = -5
			change_variable = { which = owed_steamers value = -5 }
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				check_variable = { which = owed_artillery value = 5 }
				artillery = 5
				exists = yes
			}
			artillery = -5
			change_variable = { which = owed_artillery value = -5 }
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				check_variable = { which = owed_canned_food value = 5 }
				canned_food = 5
				exists = yes
			}
			canned_food = -5
			change_variable = { which = owed_canned_food value = -5 }
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				check_variable = { which = owed_cash_money value = 1 }
				money = 10000
				exists = yes
			}
			money = -10000
			change_variable = { which = owed_cash_money value = -10 }
		}

		#release colonies that weren't annexed (soon to be deprecated, remove later)
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				has_country_flag = colony_to_be_annexed_flag
				is_vassal = yes
				exists = yes
				NOT = { has_country_modifier = colony_to_be_annexed }
				war = no
			}
			clr_country_flag = colony_to_be_annexed_flag
			country_event = 477877788
			neutrality = yes
		}

		#new round of dismantlement (soon to be deprecated, remove later)
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				has_country_modifier = colony_to_be_annexed
				is_vassal = yes
				exists = yes
				OR = {
					any_greater_power = { has_country_modifier = dismantling_country }
					any_neighbor_country = { has_country_modifier = dismantling_country }
				}
				war = no
				NOT = { has_country_modifier = considering_colonial_offer }
				ai = yes
			}
			random_list = {
                17 = { overlord = { country_event = 70005 } }
                17 = { overlord = { country_event = { id = 70005 days = 1 } } }
                17 = { overlord = { country_event = { id = 70005 days = 2 } } }
                17 = { overlord = { country_event = { id = 70005 days = 3 } } }
                17 = { overlord = { country_event = { id = 70005 days = 4 } } }
                15 = { overlord = { country_event = { id = 70005 days = 5 } } }
            }
		}
		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					ENG = {
						has_country_modifier = pax_britannica
						rank = 1
					}
					OR = {
						AND = {
							any_greater_power = { alliance_with = ENG }
							ENG = { NOT = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation } }
						}
						AND = {
							any_greater_power = { AND = { ai = yes alliance_with = ENG } }
							ENG = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation }
						}
					}
					OR = {
						TUR = {
							is_greater_power = yes
							NOT = { alliance_with = ENG }
						}
						TUR = { is_greater_power = no }
						AND = {
							ENG = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation }
							TUR = { ai = no }
						}
					}
					OR = {
						JAP = {
							is_greater_power = yes
							NOT = { alliance_with = ENG }
						}
						JAP = { is_greater_power = no }
						AND = {
							ENG = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation }
							JAP = { ai = no }
						}
					}
					OR = {
						BEL = {
							is_greater_power = yes
							NOT = { alliance_with = ENG }
						}
						BEL = { is_greater_power = no }
						AND = {
							ENG = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation }
							BEL = { ai = no }
						}
					}
					OR = {
						POR = {
							is_greater_power = yes
							NOT = { alliance_with = ENG }
						}
						POR = { is_greater_power = no }
						AND = {
							ENG = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation }
							POR = { ai = no }
						}
					}
					NOT = { exists = IRE }
					NOT = { exists = GER }
					NOT = { exists = GCF }
					NOT = { year = 1870 }
					NOT = {
						AND = {
							EGY = { war_with = TUR }
							war_with = EGY
							OR = {
								war_with = FRA
								war_with = BOR
							}
						}
					}
				}
			}
			owner = {
				random_owned = {
					limit = {
						owner = {
							ENG = { NOT = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation } }
						}
					}
					owner = {
						any_greater_power = {
							limit = {
								NOT = {
									tag = BEL
									tag = JAP
									tag = TUR
								}
								alliance_with = ENG
							}
							leave_alliance = ENG
							relation = { who = ENG value = -150 }
						}
					}
				}
				random_owned = {
					limit = {
						owner = {
							ENG = { has_country_flag = ai_splendid_isolation }
						}
					}
					owner = {
						any_greater_power = {
							limit = {
								ai = yes
								NOT = {
									tag = BEL
									tag = JAP
									tag = TUR
								}
								alliance_with = ENG
							}
							leave_alliance = ENG
							relation = { who = ENG value = -150 }
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		CLN = { country_event = { id = 477877787 days = 1 } }
	}
}

country_event = {
	id = 84393532
	title = "AI: 2nd Monthly Cleanup Check"
	desc = "AI: 2nd Monthly Cleanup Check"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Checking..."
		#abolishing serfdom
		any_country = {
            limit = {
                any_owned_province = { has_pop_type = serfs }
				exists = yes
                NOT = { debt_law = serfdom }
            }
            any_owned = {
                limit = {
                    has_pop_type = serfs
                    has_pop_type = labourers
                }
                any_pop = { limit = { type = serfs } pop_type = labourers money = 1000 }
            }
            any_owned = {
                limit = {
                    has_pop_type = serfs
                    has_pop_type = farmers
                }
                any_pop = { limit = { type = serfs } pop_type = farmers money = 1000 }
            }
            any_owned = {
                limit = {
                    has_pop_type = serfs
                    NOT = { has_pop_type = farmers has_pop_type = labourers }
                }
                any_pop = { limit = { type = serfs } pop_type = farmers money = 1000 }
            }
        }
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				ai = yes
				has_country_flag = can_use_monthly
			}
			clr_country_flag = can_use_monthly
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				ai = no
				NOT = { has_country_flag = can_use_monthly }
			}
			set_country_flag = can_use_monthly
		}
	}
}

country_event = {
	id = 47787792
	title = "AI: Biannual African Core Cleanup Check"
	desc = "AI: Biannual African Core Cleanup Check"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Checking..."
		#cleanup colonial cores
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				OR = {
					AND = {
						civilized = yes
						NOT = {
							capital_scope = { continent = africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = west_africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = central_africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = east_africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = south_africa }
						}
					}
					AND = {
						tag = CNG
						OR = {
							government = absolute_monarchy
							government = colonial_company
							government = colonial_company_2
							government = colonial_company_3
							government = colonial_company_4
						}
					}
					AND = {
						is_vassal = yes
						overlord = {
							civilized = yes
							NOT = {
								capital_scope = { continent = africa }
								capital_scope = { continent = west_africa }
								capital_scope = { continent = central_africa }
								capital_scope = { continent = east_africa }
								capital_scope = { continent = south_africa }
							}
						}
						OR = {
							capital_scope = { continent = africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = west_africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = central_africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = east_africa }
							capital_scope = { continent = south_africa }
						}
					}
				}
			}
			any_owned = {
				limit = {
                    is_core = CAR
					CAR = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
                    is_core = WAD
					WAD = { exists = no }
				}
				remove_core = WAD
			}
			any_owned = {
				limit = {
                    is_core = CAR
					CAR = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
                    is_core = SUD
					SUD = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
				}
				remove_core = SUD
			}
			any_owned = {
				limit = {
                    is_core = CAR
					CAR = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
                    is_core = DAR
					DAR = { exists = no }
				}
				remove_core = DAR
			}
			any_owned = {
				limit = {
                    is_core = CAR
					CAR = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
                    is_core = AZA
					AZA = { exists = no }
				}
				remove_core = AZA
			}
			any_owned = {
				limit = {
                    is_core = NGR
					NGR = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
                    is_core = SOK
					SOK = { exists = no }
				}
				remove_core = SOK
			}
			any_owned = {
				limit = {
                    is_core = NGR
					NGR = { OR = { exists = no is_vassal = yes } }
                    is_core = DND
					DND = { exists = no }
				}
				remove_core = DND
			}
			any_owned = {

country_event = {
	id = 477877791
	title = "AI: Yearly Cleanup Check"
	desc = "AI: Yearly Cleanup Check"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Checking..."
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				ai = no
			}
			set_country_flag = can_use_monthly
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				ai = yes
			}
			clr_country_flag = can_use_monthly
		}
		any_land_province = {
			limit = {
				has_province_modifier = capital_mobilisation
				OR = {

					}
				}

		#upgrade rebels
		random_owned = {
			limit = {
				owner = {
					year = 1880
					NOT = { has_global_flag = rebel_tech_1850 }
				}
			}
			owner = {
				REB = {
					activate_technology = post_napoleonic_thought
					activate_technology = flintlock_rifles
					activate_technology = muzzle_loaded_rifles
					activate_technology = bronze_muzzle_loaded_artillery
					activate_technology = military_staff_system
					activate_technology = army_command_principle
				}
				set_global_flag = rebel_tech_1850
				2518 = { add_core = PHL remove_core = YEM }
				2525 = { add_core = VTU remove_core = YEM }
				2579 = { add_core = VTU remove_core = YEM }

country_event = {
	id = 477877788
	title = "Freedom"
	desc = "We have acquired independence!"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Nice."
		overlord = { release_vassal = THIS }
	}
}

country_event = {
	id = 477877789
	title = "AI: Cleanup Setup"
	desc = "AI: Cleanup Setup"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Cleanup Setup"
		CLN = {
			country_event = 477877787
			country_event = 477877790
			country_event = 477877791
			add_country_modifier = { name = neutrality_modifier duration = -1 }
		}
	}
}

##vassal interactions events

country_event = {
	id = 477877792
	title = "Vassal Interactions: $FROMCOUNTRY$"
	desc = "If $FROMCOUNTRY$ is the country you want to interact with, select an option. Otherwise, select 'Next country' to cycle through, or select 'Exit options' to return to the game."

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Release this country"
		FROM = {
			country_event = 477877788
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				exists = yes
				vassal_of = THIS
			}
			clr_country_flag = interacted_with
		}
	}

	option = {
		name = "Return cores to this country"
		any_owned = {
			limit = {
				is_core = FROM
				NOT = { is_core = THIS }
			}
			secede_province = FROM
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				exists = yes
				vassal_of = THIS
			}
			clr_country_flag = interacted_with
		}
	}

	option = {
		name = "Next country"
		random_country = {
			limit = {
				vassal_of = THIS
				exists = yes
				NOT = { has_country_flag = interacted_with }
			}
			country_event = 477877793
			THIS = { set_country_flag = possible_interactions }
		}
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				vassal_of = THIS
				exists = yes
				THIS = { NOT = { has_country_flag = possible_interactions } }
			}
			clr_country_flag = interacted_with
		}
	}

	option = {
		name = "Exit options"
		any_country = {
			limit = {
				exists = yes
				vassal_of = THIS
			}
			clr_country_flag = interacted_with
		}
	}
}

country_event = {
	id = 477877793
	title = "AI: Vassal Interactions"
	desc = "This event lets your overlord interact with you. If you are a player, just close this."

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "OK"
		set_country_flag = interacted_with
		FROM = { clr_country_flag = possible_interactions }
		overlord = { country_event = 477877792 }
	}
}

#some new colonial organization events
country_event = {
	id = 477877794
	title = "Organization of Gambia"
	desc = "With our control over Gambia secured, our colonial administration in the area has consolidated their hold. New maps have been drawn, and an official protectorate has been established."
	picture = "colonial_nigeria"

	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = "Excellent."
		GMB = { all_core = { remove_core = GMB } }
		1785 = { add_core = GMB }
		1890 = { add_core = GMB }
		3961 = { add_core = GMB }

		any_owned = {
			limit = { is_core = GMB }
			remove_core = TOO
			remove_core = WOL
			remove_core = SEG
			remove_core = TOU
			remove_core = GBU
		}

		GMB = {
			clr_country_flag = sunni_country
			clr_country_flag = shiite_country
			clr_country_flag = ibadi_country
			clr_country_flag = catholic_country
			clr_country_flag = protestant_country
			clr_country_flag = mormon_country
			clr_country_flag = orthodox_country
			clr_country_flag = coptic_country
			clr_country_flag = jewish_country
			clr_country_flag = yazidi_country
			clr_country_flag = mahayana_country
			clr_country_flag = gelugpa_country
			clr_country_flag = theravada_country
			clr_country_flag = hindu_country
			clr_country_flag = shinto_country
			clr_country_flag = sikh_country
			clr_country_flag = animist_country
		}

		random_owned = { limit = { owner = { has_country_flag = catholic_country } } GMB = { religion = catholic set_country_flag = catholic_country } }
		random_owned = { limit = { owner = { has_country_flag = protestant_country } } GMB = { religion = protestant set_country_flag = protestant_country } }

country_event = {
	id = 477877795
	title = "Organization of Timor"
	desc = "With our control over Timor secured, our colonial administration in the area has consolidated their hold. New maps have been drawn, and an official protectorate has been established."

		name = "Excellent."

			limit = {
				NOT = { is_core = INO }

				}

			add_core = TMR
		}

			clr_country_flag = sunni_country
